// Read-path field exposure: a customer's `loyaltyTier` must travel on the
// public-profile read path — it is included in the read projection (the Prisma
// `select` the profile query asks for) AND returned in the API response shape.
// The exposure site is `readPublicProfile` / `renderPublicProfile` in
// code/src/services/customers.profile.service.ts. This is the reliably
// code-derivable core of "the tier reaches the consumer" — a projection +
// response SITE, not prop threading through named files.

field-exposure customer.loyalty-tier-exposed {
  origin "reference/specs/modules/customers/data.md" "Customer read projection" 43..50
  field Entity:Customer.loyaltyTier
  via query-select
  via api-response
  in readPublicProfile
}
